---
// AboutMe component - shows information about the user
---

<div id="about-me-modal" class="about-modal hidden">
  <div class="about-content">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
      Hello! I'm a passionate developer who loves creating beautiful and functional web experiences. 
      I enjoy working with modern technologies and building projects that make a difference.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, reading about design patterns, 
      or working on personal projects that challenge me to grow as a developer.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about-modal {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 15;
    opacity: 1;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-modal.hidden {
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 90%;
    color: white;
    font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  p:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      margin: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
